ed="T" n="0830c18"/><persName key="A012344">釋抱玉</persName>者，行業高奇，人事罕接。每言來事，<lb
ed="T" n="0830c19"/>如目擊焉。見<name>釋</name>子<persName key="A013564">大光</persName>而誨之曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A013564">汝</ref>誦經<lb
ed="T" n="0830c20"/>宜高揭法音，徹諸天傾聽，必得神人輔<lb
ed="T" n="0830c21"/>翼。」後皆符其記莂<ptr target="#n543"/>。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京邑</ref>歸信千計。每夕獨<lb
ed="T" n="0830c22"/>處一室，闔扉撤燭。甞有僧於門隙間窺<lb
ed="T" n="0830c23"/>其所以，見<persName key="A012344">玉</persName>口中出慶雲，華彩可愛。後<lb
ed="T" n="0830c24"/>年可九十許而終。終時方大暑，而尸無萎<lb
ed="T" n="0830c25"/>敗。宰臣<persName key="A010311">第五琦</persName>與<persName key="A012344">玉</persName>相善，及終，臨喪頗哀。<lb
ed="T" n="0830c26"/><persName key="A010311">琦</persName>以香乳灌其口，隨有祥光自口而出，晃<lb
ed="T" n="0830c27"/>然四照。<persName key="A010311">琦</persName>愈奇之<ptr target="#n544"/>。<persName key="A010311">琦</persName><date from-iso="+0759-11-29" key="j19986111998639" to-iso="+0759-12-27"><name>乾元</name>二年十<supplied resp="sgsz">一</supplied>月</date>貶<placeName key="PL000000034410">忠州</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0830c28"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>刺</sic><corr>長</corr></choice>史<ptr target="#n2498"/>。<date notBefore-iso="+0762-05-17" key="j19995111999761" notAfter-iso="+0763-01-22"><name>寶應</name>初</date>入為太子賓客，至<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>尹<ptr target="#n2499"/>，<persName key="A012344">玉</persName>皆<lb
ed="T" n="0830c29"/>預言榮貴轗𨎺<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1704"/>相半，皆如其言，刻意歸信<pb ed="T" n="0831a" xml:id="T50.2061.0831a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0831a01"/>焉。</p>
